5000|$|Super Bell"Z (read [...] "Super Bellz") is a {{group known}} for its [...] "DJ Train Conductor" [...] songs in which they lay sounds of trains, station fuss, etc., and voice {{recorded}} to resemble <b>train</b> <b>announcements</b> over hip hop beats. They were under contract with Toshiba-EMI, but in 2005 they went independent.|$|R
